.TH smi-diskless-useradd "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Diskless Command"
.SH NAME
smi-diskless-useradd \- Add a user to a diskless environment
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-diskless-useradd
.I DISKLESS_NAME
.I USER_NAME
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B smi-diskless-useradd
adds a new user to the specified \fIDISKLESS_NAME\fR environment.
It performs a \fBchroot\fR(8) into the diskless root directory and executes \fBuseradd\fR(8).
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
Command written by Imre Tabur.
Documentation written by Junie.
.SH "REPORTING BUGS"
.PP
Report smi-diskless-useradd bugs to \fIinfo@setmy.info\fR
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.PP
